data.description: WOW 3.5% towards buyers downpayment assistance or pre-paid closing cost. For this stunning Mediterranean- Inspired single-family home located at 2449 Matheson Ave in Spring Hill, Florida 34608. Boasting an elegant design, this residence offers 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, with pool, and bonus flex space for an office or extra room, it spans across 1,699 square feet of spacious living. Built 1988, this timeless gem embodies the allure of Mediterranean architecture, blending classic charm with modern comfort. Enjoy the Florida sun.... The perfect space to entertain or relax by the inground pool and lanai and to create those memories that will last a lifetime.
